# ai-copilot-serve Cursor Rules

This project is a local control-plane service. Keep routers thin, business logic in services, external integrations behind adapters, and all risky local execution behind Workspace Guard and Approval Runtime.

Use these boundaries:

- API routers: request parsing, dependency injection, response mapping only.
- Services: orchestration and state transitions.
- Repositories: database operations only.
- Integrations: Hermes, Team Hub, shell, filesystem, and other external systems.
- Runtime: process registry, port allocation, gateway lifecycle, heartbeat, locks.

Before editing code, inspect `AGENTS.md` and the relevant skill under `.cursor/skills/`.
